{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we arrived here, people couldn't understand that people came over here practically penniless and they traveled first class.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very hard to explain to Americans here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Preparation, I don't remember any other preparations except a few hasty English lessons by a student, just a few words of English.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In gymnasium, I did study French and Latin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the second grade, [NON-ENGLISH], when I left, and that was equivalent of-- what is it-- fifth, sixth grade, I guess.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I continued and we didn't learn any English in the Hebrew school, in the religious school-- in the-- in the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just learned [? general ?] things and practical things like farming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they told us there was a little plot of earth and we planted some radishes and-- and lettuce because many of the people had plans to go to Palestine at the time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there they would have become farmers most likely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So a little bit of practical work, which was a good thing, actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shop, carpentry, a few practical things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's-- otherwise, I don't-- the lessons were very general because many grades were put together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it's a little difficult to teach in a two-room school that have many different grades.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was a great adventure for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I looked at the whole thing-- of course, it was different for my parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very sad and their-- they didn't know what the future would hold for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was looking forward to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was sorry in a way that we weren't coming to Palestine, but my mother always said, can you imagine your father as a farmer?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You must be out of your mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And there was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
